Once upon a time, in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree, which was on the banks of a river.
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day the crocodile ca,e to the banks of the river and rested under theberry tree.
The kindhearted monkey offered him some berries. The crocodile liked the berries and they became very good friends as the crocodile started visiting him everyday.